<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hesap360 | Kredi, Mevduat ve Kart Karşılaştırma Merkezi</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root { 
            --bg: #020617; 
            --surface: #0f172a; 
            --primary: #3b82f6; 
            --primary-glow: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
            --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08); 
            --text-dim: #94a3b8; 
        }

        body { 
            background: var(--bg); font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; color: #fff; margin: 0; 
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 50% -20%, var(--primary-glow) 0%, transparent 50%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }

        /* Header & Logo */
        nav { padding: 30px 0; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
        .logo { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: -1px; }
        .logo span { color: var(--primary); }

        /* Hero Bölümü */
        .hero { padding: 60px 0 40px; text-align: center; }
        .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 1.1; }
        .hero h1 span { color: var(--primary); }
        .hero p { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }

        /* Ana Servis Izgarası */
        .services-grid { 
            display: grid; 
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); 
            gap: 20px; 
            margin-top: 50px; 
        }

        .service-card {
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 28px;
            padding: 35px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-start;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .service-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);
        }

        .service-card i {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background: var(--primary-glow);
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 16px;
        }

        .service-card h3 { font-size: 1.4rem; margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-weight: 700; }
        .service-card p { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }

        /* "Yeni" Etiketi */
        .badge {
            position: absolute; top: 20px; right: 20px;
            background: var(--primary); color: #fff; font-size: 0.65rem;
            padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 20px; font-weight: 800;
        }

        /* Footer Alt Bilgi */
        footer { 
            margin-top: 100px; padding: 40px 0; text-align: center; 
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero { padding: 40px 0; }
            .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <nav>
        <a href="/" class="logo">HESAP<span>360</span></a>
        <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-dim); font-weight: 600;">2026 GÜNCEL VERİ SİSTEMİ</div>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero">
        <h1>Finansal Analizde<br><span>Yeni Standart.</span></h1>
        <p>HangiKredi ve Hesap Kurdu kalitesinde, reklamsız ve en hızlı hesaplama araçları.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="services-grid">
        <a href="/kredi" class="service-card">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group"></i>
            <h3>Kredi Karşılaştır</h3>
            <p>Tüm bankaların güncel faizlerini tek ekranda analiz et ve ödeme planını çıkar.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/mevduat" class="service-card">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line"></i>
            <h3>Mevduat Getirisi</h3>
            <p>Paranıza en yüksek faizi veren bankayı bul, stopaj kesintisini anında hesapla.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/kredi-limit" class="service-card">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-gauge-high"></i>
            <h3>Limit Tahmini</h3>
            <p>Banka rasyolarına göre ne kadar kredi çekebileceğini saniyeler içinde öğren.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/kredi-karti" class="service-card">
            <span class="badge">YENİ</span>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-credit-card"></i>
            <h3>Kredi Kartı Analizi</h3>
            <p>Asgari ödeme tutarı, gecikme faizi ve limit politikalarını analiz edin.</p>
        </a>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>© 2026 Hesap360 | Profesyonel Finansal Çözümler Merkezi</p>
        <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
            <i class="fa-brands fa-cc-visa"></i> &nbsp; <i class="fa-brands fa-cc-mastercard"></i> &nbsp; <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i>
        </div>
    </footer>
</div>

</body>
</html>
